The paper focuses on the impact of culture on the requirements engineering process, which is a key aspect of software engineering. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses the communication between stakeholders, which is related to Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper mentions cybersecurity concerns, which could fall under cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy). The paper also discusses the adaptation of the RE process, which could fall under cs.CE (Computing Education) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
